cu.explanation_en: Setting the CU's NGU IP address to the same as the AMF IP (192.168.70.132) will cause IP address conflicts, preventing proper network interface configuration and leading to connection failures.

du.explanation_en: Setting the gNB name to an empty string will cause identification issues and prevent proper gNB registration.
du.explanation_zh: 將 gNB 名稱設定為空字符串會導致識別問題，並阻止正確的 gNB 註冊。
